'''''And Her Tears Flowed Like Wine''''' is a [[popular song]] and [[jazz standard]] first published in [[1944 in music|1944]].

The lyrics were written by [[Joe Greene]], with music composition by [[Stan Kenton]] and Charles Lawrence.

Probably the best known version of the song was recorded in 1944 by [[Anita O'Day]] along with Kenton's orchestra. A version was also recorded by [[Ella Fitzgerald]] the following year.

